/**
 * ThemeSelect — intentionally empty.
 *
 * The user-facing theme switcher was removed (issue #32). Theme tracks
 * `prefers-color-scheme` exclusively, with a dark fallback. The boot
 * script in `docs/astro.config.mjs` (Starlight `head` array) sets
 * `data-theme` before paint and re-syncs on live OS-pref changes.
 *
 * This file exists so Starlight's component-override registration
 * (`COMPONENT_OVERRIDES` in `packages/starlight-theme/core/config/
 * override.ts`) maps ThemeSelect → an empty component, suppressing
 * Starlight's default toggle without forcing an exclusion list. Header
 * no longer imports or renders this; the export stays for the
 * component-override slot.
 */
